no.motif

Class Implicits

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.motif.Implicits

  • public final class Implicits
extends Object
    This class is used to set certain implicit values, which are usually global for larger scopes, e.g. the whole runtime, the context of a web request, etc. Instead of passing these values for each function call, they can be set here as resolvers (Fn0s), for relevant functions to request their values.
